Description	The savings account product may share many features with a standard bank current account (e.g. standing orders, direct debits, payments and deposit services) with some constraints/limitations. There can be restrictions on the amount and frequency of withdrawals with an associated fee/penalty structure to offset higher interest benefits. Sweep mechanisms linked to other products (current account) can also be supported.	Taxation Rules	Attributes for handling customer taxation and reporting	E	E	E						E								I					I			E	IE					IE			E	E	E		E					E	E	E				IE			E	IE	E				IE			E	E	E		E		IE			E	IE	E					E		E
