Description	This service domain tracks the state of a party relationship with the bank from the initial checks made when establishing a new business relationship with a customer or partner and then that are performed as necessary over the duration of the relationship. The checks and the maintenance requirements will vary by party type (e.g. individual, company, partner) and jurisdiction. The checks cover bank specific and legal and regulatory considerations and may be updated based on a standard schedule or by request in specific circumstances.	Regulatory Regulations	Attributes for regulations that are applied in regulatory assessments by the service center in production	E	E	E	E		E	E		E								I								E	I								E	I	E				E	E		E	I	E							E																											
