Description	The Servicing Mandate service domain maintains an agreement between the bank and an external party that governs/constrains the allowed access given to the bank's products and services. This access permission can be defined at two levels - overall for the service provider and at a more detailed level as applied to a specific customer. 			E	E	E	E			E	E	E								IE	E	E	E				E	E																																																						
