Description	Case resolution tasks follow specific procedures for the type of case involved. Case resolution can be quick by applying resolution rules and obtaining additional authorization as necessary, or they can be long living activities, for example where documentation is requested and has to be retrieved from merchants or other interested parties before the disputed issue can finally be ruled upon. A wide range of case types can be expected			E	E	E	E		E	E		E								I	E							E	I	E							E	I	E		E					E																																				
