Description	"This service domain handles the distribution and operation of a client device based/resident facility to support local working and access to the banks different products and services. It allows for the customer to maintain information and configuration settings remotely to govern their own access environment as necessary. The service domain operates outside the bank but is included in the landscape as it may run application capabilities that are either provided by or certified for use by the bank.
"			E	E	E						E								E			E					E	E								E	E					E			E	E	E				E	E		E	E	E				E	E		E																		
