A customer downloads an end-user financial management application offered by the bank
"			IO	IO							O	CR Customer Workbench Operating Session Instance Record	Customer Workbench Operating Session Instance Record					An operating session of the customer resident application with various types of interaction with the bank	IO								O	IO								O	IO								O	IO								O	IO								O																		
